!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80
title CMP-07 - Errori, trace e audit
skinparam shadowing false

component "AuthorizationService.require" as Require
component "ACLService" as AclService
component "AuthorizationPolicy.explain" as Explain
component "Denied / validation mapper" as Mapper
queue "Audit sink" as Audit
component "DecisionTrace" as Trace

Require --> Mapper : AuthenticationError\nAuthorizationDenied
AclService --> Mapper : ACLValidationError\nGrantConstraintError
Explain --> Trace
Trace --> Audit : trace amministrativa
AclService --> Audit : ACL_ENTRY_*
Require --> Audit : AUTHZ_DENIED

note bottom of Audit
  Eventi minimi:
  AUTHZ_DENIED, ACL_ENTRY_CREATED,
  ACL_ENTRY_UPDATED, ACL_ENTRY_DELETED,
  PROFILE_CHANGED, BOOTSTRAP_COMPLETED.
end note

legend
  Vedi anche: [[../use%20case/07_spiegare_decisione_audit.puml UC-07]] |
  [[../classi/07_errori_audit_trace.puml Classi errori/audit]]
endlegend
@enduml
